$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 SIT2 {
  coords 1633.899 30.024 7729.971
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2>"\
  "DTL: 05/01/1991, 0800hr, Al-Hadra, Kuwait."\
  "Weather: Clear, no forecast of change."\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2>"\
  "Coalition forces continue offensive operations into Kuwait as Iraqi units attempt to regroup and reinforce fragmented positions across the region. Intelligence reports indicate an Iraqi mechanised force is moving toward Al-Hadra with the intention of bypassing coalition lines and linking up with a sister company operating further north."\
  "British forces have been ordered to fight through the dense urban districts of the city and secure the northern highway before the reinforcements can break through. Iraqi defenders already positioned throughout Al-Hadra are expected to resist heavily, using the city itself to delay the advance and buy time for incoming forces."\
  "Control of the highway will determine whether the Iraqi reinforcements reach their objective — or are stopped inside the city."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 CS2 {
  coords 1633.899 30.024 7729.971
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>CALLSIGNS</h2>"\
  "• HQ - Shako50"\
  "• 1st Squad - Shako51"\
  "• 2nd Squad - Shako52"\
  "• 3rd Squad - Shako53"\
  "• AT Group - Shako54"\
  ""\
  "<h2>FREQ/CHAN</h2>"\
  "• All callsigns - 42hz"\
  ""\
  "<h2>PASSWORDS</h2>"\
  "All can be changed at CO's discretion."\
  "• <b>Challenge:</b> Purple | <b>Password:</b> Burglar"\
  "• Running password: 88"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 EF2 {
  coords 1633.899 30.024 7729.971
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2> "\
  "Enemy forces are the British, 3rd Battalion, Royal Regiment of Fusiliers.  Staging at GRID: 040045"\
  "We estimate the staging element to be roughly 70x dismounted troops from their fighting vehicles which are maintaining a cordon around the city."\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2> "\
  "• Almost all enemy troops have optics for their weapons compared to us who don't."\
  "• Large supply of ammo and equipment."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FF2 {
  coords 1633.899 30.024 7729.971
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "We are 5th Platoon from the Glorious Shako Company, 5th Battalion.  "\
  "Consisting of 26 active personnel, with three wounded currently resting at the staging area. These three will reinforce any losses."\
  "Currently staged at flag marker, GRID: 044050.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• We have the ability to hold position and wait for enemy contact. Theres no need to counter attack."\
  "• 1x BTR is positioned to deny freedom of movement along the dual carriageway, while also providing us with control over movement along the same axis.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>SERVICE & SUPPORT</h2>  "\
  "A supply crate is available at the staging area containing:  "\
  "• 12x HE grenades and 5x smoke grenades  "\
  "• 30x assorted rifle magazines  "\
  "• 1x periscope  "
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 MIS2 {
  coords 1633.899 30.024 7729.971
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>  "\
  "Our mission is to conduct a DELAY of advancing British forces in order to prevent them from occupying the highway to deny a passing friendly formation in 45mins."\
  ""\
  "<h2>MISSION DESCRIPTION</h2>  "\
  "A friendly mechanised element will attempt to bypass coalition forces by moving around the rear of the city via the highway, with the intent to link up with a sister company north of Al-Hadra.  "\
  ""\
  "British forces are advancing rapidly through the city with speed and aggression in an attempt to reach and occupy the highway, thereby disrupting friendly movement.  "\
  ""\
  "We must delay their advance long enough to allow the mechanised element to bypass the city and continue its movement unimpeded."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
}